I used a ESP8266 Feather Huzzah for this project.
Pin connections

Feather ---> A4988

16 ------> EN

0 --------> DIR

13 ------> STEP

GND ---> GND

3V ------> VDD



A4988 ----> Stepper Motor

1B ----> Blue

1A ----> Red

2A ----> Green

2B ----> Black

The RESET and SLEEP pins on the motor driver also want a wire connecting the two together.
